"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"*Originally Published - July 19, 2021*\\n\\n![ETHCC Hackathon](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Ej2p7C4QC_Kyco8zhrNIP.png?height=655&width=1060)\\n\\n**Welcome to the fourth edition of the Upshot Update üëã**\\n\\nIn this newsletter we‚Äôll round-up the latest news, updates and insights from the team, and take a look at what‚Äôs happening across the NFT space.\\n\\nIf you haven‚Äôt already, make sure you [subscribe to our bi-weekly newsletter](http://eepurl.com/hgllNn) so that you don‚Äôt miss a beat. Let‚Äôs dive in üëá\\n\\n## üá´üá∑ Upshot in Paris\\n\\nInnovation in the crypto space is born out global events that bring the community together to interact, build, and exchange ideas. Join us for a week in Paris as we work to build the future of DeFi x NFTs together!\\n\\n## F√™te DAO üéâ presented by Uniswap and Upshot\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0\\\\*3LhSsXJddXJ-Zww-.jpeg)\\n\\nF√™te szn has arrived. Kick off ETH CC with [F√™te DAO](https://www.fetedao.io/) ‚Äî a night of talks, drinks, and music on the roof of the Tour Montparnasse in Paris. Featuring a panel discussion with Upshot founder Nick Emmons, Aave CEO Stani Kulechov, and Uniswap Head of Growth Ashleigh Schap. Followed by performances from Polo & Pan and Pat Lok.\\n\\nüìç Tour Montparnasse, Paris\\n\\nüìÖ Tuesday, July 20 @ 8PM\\n\\n## Build the Future of DeFi üõ† at EthCC Hackathon 2021\\n\\nDive into DAO x DeFi x NFT summer with EthCC Hackathon 2021. We are excited to bring together irl and online developers, creatives, and experts to work on the future of finance in Paris! Join in-person to work with sponsors and mentors directly, or if you are participating online join the sponsor Discord channels for support.\\n\\nüìÖ July 23‚Äì25\\n\\n‚úçÔ∏è Register on [Gitcoin](https://gitcoin.co/hackathon/ethcc/onboard)\\n\\n***Plus‚Ä¶***\\n\\n* Upshot founder Nick Emmons will be speaking about the intersection of DeFi and NFTs at Bunchy Protocol‚Äôs [NFT Financialization event ](https://www.eventbrite.fr/e/nft-financialization-tickets-163505239573)on July 20 @ 5:30PM.\\n\\n## üí° Insights\\n\\nAnswering questions on Upshot is simple, addicting, and gas-free. In this short tutorial you‚Äôll learn how to create an account on Upshot, bridge funds to Polygon, and get started appraising NFTs.\\n\\n## üñº NFT Round-Up\\n\\n## What‚Äôs Happening ‚ö°Ô∏è\\n\\n* NFT sales volume surged to $2.5 billion in the first half of the year, with volume on OpenSea setting a monthly record in June, according to Reuters. Check out the [full report](https://decrypt.co/75301/nft-sales-volumes-hit-2-5-billion-for-first-half-of-2021) for more stats.\\n* Andrew Steinwold had [DC Investor on Zima Red](https://anchor.fm/andrew-steinwold/episodes/Aftab--DC-Investor---Defi--NFTs--Ethereum-Community-Member---Zima-Red-ep-62-e13qqb3) to discuss NFT financialization and DAOs.\\n* NFTX launched [V2 of the protocol](https://blog.nftx.org/introducing-nftx-v2/), aiming to bring NFTX closer to becoming the liquidity hub for the DeFi x NFT ecosystem.\\n* Foundation now features the [top 100 collectors](https://foundation.app/trending?tab=collectors) on the platform.\\n* Bored Ape Yacht Club held a [Kennel Club dog show](https://twitter.com/AxieKing/status/1408451699207917571?s=20), giving 10,000 dogs to ape holders.\\n\\n## Top NFT Sales (Last 7 Days)\\\\* üíé\\n\\n1\\\\. [CryptoPunk #8870](https://opensea.io/assets/0xb47e3cd837ddf8e4c57f05d70ab865de6e193bbb/8870?ref=0xcd2b3c517d3de4f962dc01700dc57960cdbeb5e9) | 200 ETH ($397k)\\n\\n2\\\\. [CryptoPunk #5002](https://opensea.io/assets/0xb47e3cd837ddf8e4c57f05d70ab865de6e193bbb/5002?ref=0xcd2b3c517d3de4f962dc01700dc57960cdbeb5e9) | 205 ETH ($386k)\\n\\n3\\\\. [CryptoPunk #5690](https://opensea.io/assets/0xb47e3cd837ddf8e4c57f05d70ab865de6e193bbb/5690?ref=0xcd2b3c517d3de4f962dc01700dc57960cdbeb5e9) | 57 ETH ($354k)\\n\\n## Top NFT Collections (Last 7 Days)\\\\* üñº\\n\\n1\\\\. [Axie Infinity](https://dappradar.com/ethereum/games/axie-infinity) | Vol: $176.5M (+7%) | Sales: 315k (-4%)\\n\\n2\\\\. [Bored Ape Yacht Club](https://dappradar.com/ethereum/collectibles/bored-ape-yacht-club) | Vol: $19.4M (+284%) | Sales: 1,450 (+167%)\\n\\n3\\\\. [CryptoPunks](https://dappradar.com/ethereum/collectibles/cryptopunks) | Vol: $13.8M (+6%) | Sales: 210 (+10%)\\n\\n\\\\*Data from \\\\**[DappRadar](https://dappradar.com/nft)*\\n\\n## üë• Come Work With Us\\n\\nUpshot is hiring across multiple roles!\\n\\nWe are a team of crypto-natives with deep experience working on some of the leading projects in the space ‚Äî backed by the foremost funds and angels in crypto. At Upshot, we are committed to finding top talent looking to make an impact at the forefront of this burgeoning space.\\n\\nInterested in working at Upshot? Check out our [open positions](https://jobs.lever.co/upshot.io) üë•\\n\\n## Join the üÜôüèÄ Community\\n\\nHop in the [Upshot Discord](https://discord.gg/upshot) to chat about all things NFTs with the team and fellow collectors! We‚Äôre building a collector-centric community and would love to have you be a part of it.\\n\\n## Stay in the loop!\\n\\n* Join us on [Discord](https://discord.gg/xNeh7vzXTQ)\\n* Follow us on [Twitter](https://twitter.com/UpshotHQ)\\n* Subscribe to our [newsletter](http://eepurl.com/hgllNn)\",\"timestamp\":1637607534,\"title\":\"Upshot Update: EthCC Paris and NFT Round-Up - UpshotHQ\"},\"digest\":\"IT_sd0NIMTt7H4KwRSI_GXO_KCQPi6u5ALGS5WIWk9o\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x82FE4757D134a56BFC7968A0f0d1635345053104\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"70YDdZt7UkapAbIrgck8lxDFj7btCa_BnsnkxQ9TUbQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"HALfPZUZAd6pZtK9LcxbUpPBouuP5Pm0UfKtuOdeIII\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"IRxFwp7w6dtpRFO7iimuuf2FANJVoCmGJ7sy_n0JB_DajkCxAfsJL18ne8thbD2J2xlLcmDxogvwI1JbbCsxpQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xb319b5679697e95aa7fb0a88e16f37632c0ce